    "description": "PBsystems,Inc. engages in the cloud infrastructure business in Japan. The company operates through Secure Cloud System and Emotional System segments. It provides hybrid cloud construction technology, focusing on the cloudification of business systems and SaaS operators' online service infrastructure; cybersecurity, protect against system failures and cyberattacks; and Smart Factory. The company also manufacture and sells MetaWalkers, a VR device for a 360-degree virtual space experience without the need to wear VR goggles; MetaAnywhere, a video device that projects images freed from the limitations of the conventional cylindrical image projection; as well as metaverse for companies and local governments. PBsystems,Inc. was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Fukuoka, Japan."
